events.name: Temple Owls at Duke Blue Devils

headlines.description: Daniel Jones threw for 423 yards and five touchdowns, T.J. Rahming caught 12 passes for 240 yards and two scores, and Duke blew past Temple 56-27 in the Independence Bowl on Thursday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Jones, Duke offense roll past Temple in Independence Bowl

video.headline: Jones throws for five TDs, runs for another in blowout

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Jones throws for 5 TD, runs in another in blowout) 2018/12/27 ESHEET SOTFULL

headlines.description: Jonathan Taylor ran for 205 yards and a touchdown and topped the 2,000-yard season mark to help Wisconsin rout Miami 35-3 in a chilly Pinstripe Bowl on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Taylor runs for 205 yards in Wisconsin's Pinstripe victory

video.headline: Taylor's 41-yard run sets up Wisconsin TD

headlines.description: Charlie Brewer threw for 384 yards and two touchdowns, the second a tiebreaking 52-yarder in the fourth quarter, and ran for 109 yards and another score to help Baylor beat Vanderbilt 45-38 in the Texas Bowl on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Brewer helps Baylor beat Vanderbilt 45-38 in Texas Bowl

video.headline: Brewer links up with Jones for 52-yard Baylor TD
